# Playwright CLI Workflow

- Use `playwright-cli` for browser automation tasks in this project.
- Prefer `npm run pw:*` scripts for common operations (`open`, `snapshot`, `screenshot`, `console`, `network`, `close`).
- When validating UI changes, capture at least one `snapshot` and one `screenshot`.
- Reuse the short session name `sf` unless a test requires isolation.
- Keep browser automation focused on user-facing flows: screen navigation, 3D rendering visibility, and AI verdict path.
